WEBVTT

00:02:56.200 --> 00:03:00.056
And now we've got
these fearmongering politicians

00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:02.256
that keep trying to pass
these bathroom bills.

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:03.616
Have you heard about these?

00:03:03.640 --> 00:03:06.416
They try to legislate
to try and force people like myself

00:03:06.440 --> 00:03:11.136
to use the bathroom
that they deem most appropriate

00:03:11.160 --> 00:03:13.696
according to the gender
I was assigned at birth.

00:03:13.720 --> 00:03:17.216
And if these politicians
ever get their way,

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:20.736
in Arizona or California or Florida

00:03:20.760 --> 00:03:23.136
or just last week in Houston, Texas,

00:03:23.160 --> 00:03:24.360
or Ottawa,

00:03:24.880 --> 00:03:30.680
well then, using the men's room
will not be a legal option for me either.